Invocation Name: my daily reading
des:
Ask for your daily tarot reading to better understand what the cosmos has in store for you.

The Major Arcana Daily Tarot is a great skill for beginners in the world of tarot reading, and provides basic descriptions for those card that fall within the major arcana.

To start, just say "Alexa, ask my daily reading to draw my daily card".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
